You are working on the CodeSage project. Read `AGENTS.md` first for complete project conventions.

Key rules:
- Backend: FastAPI + async SQLAlchemy + PostgreSQL + Redis + LightRAG 1.5.3
- Frontend: Vue 3 + TypeScript + Element Plus + Tailwind CSS 4 + Pinia
- All RAG code lives in `backend/rag/`, never scatter in services/schemas/endpoints
- All AI prompts live in `backend/sys_prompts/*.md`, never hardcode in .py files
- Architecture: endpoints → services → models (strict layering)
- Python: snake_case; TS/Vue: camelCase/PascalCase
- Vue 3 el-form ref must use function binding: `:ref="(el) => { formRef = el }"`
- LightRAG uses lazy singleton pattern, never init at startup
- File upload to RAG: frontend reads text → POST JSON to /rag/upload-file
- Chunking/vectorization all delegated to LightRAG native ainsert(), no custom splitting
